column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.RA, p.DEC, p.MPE, p.MP2#, r.cModelMag_u, r.cModelMagErr_u, r.cModelMag_g, r.cModelMagErr_g, r.cModelMag_r, r.cModelMagErr_r, r.cModelMag_i, r.cModelMagErr_i, r.cModelMag_z, r.cModelMagErr_z, r.deVRad_u, r.deVRadErr_u, r.deVRad_g, r.deVRadErr_g, r.deVRad_r, r.deVRadErr_r, r.deVRad_i, r.deVRadErr_i, r.deVRad_z, r.deVRadErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN RC3 p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN PhotoObjAll r ON r.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
